---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Monovus privacy policy."
>
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-electric-cyan font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-12">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">What We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            This site collects minimal data. Cloudflare provides privacy-respecting
            analytics — aggregate page views, referrers, and browser information. Standard
            web server logs capture IP addresses, request paths, and timestamps. No
            personal information is collected beyond what you voluntarily provide via email.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">How It's Used</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            Analytics data helps us understand how the site is used. Server logs support
            security monitoring and troubleshooting. If you email us, we use your information
            solely to respond to your inquiry.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            The site uses Cloudflare for content delivery, security, and analytics.
            Google Fonts is used for web font delivery. Each service operates under
            its own privacy policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            This site does not use first-party cookies for tracking. Cloudflare may set
            technical cookies necessary for security and performance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal
            information we hold. Contact us at
            <a href="mailto:hello@monovus.solutions" class="text-electric-cyan hover:text-electric-cyan-dark">hello@monovus.solutions</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Changes</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            This policy may be updated from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
            Questions about this policy:
            <a href="mailto:hello@monovus.solutions" class="text-electric-cyan hover:text-electric-cyan-dark">hello@monovus.solutions</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
